# App Layout Structure

This wiki application is built with Next.js and uses PayloadCMS for content management. The layout follows a clean, minimalist design with a focus on content.

## Key Layout Components

- **Root Layout**: The main layout wrapper is in [src/app/(home)/layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/(home)/layout.tsx), which sets up the page structure with a background pattern and container.

- **Header**: The site header is defined in [src/components/Header.tsx](mdc:src/components/Header.tsx) and displays the site name, subtitle, and optional breadcrumb.

- **Footer**: The minimal footer is in [src/components/Footer.tsx](mdc:src/components/Footer.tsx) and shows a disclaimer text.

- **Search**: Search functionality is implemented in [src/components/Search.tsx](mdc:src/components/Search.tsx).

- **Toolbar**: Additional UI controls are in [src/components/Toolbar.tsx](mdc:src/components/Toolbar.tsx).

## Page Structure

- **Home Page**: [src/app/(home)/page.tsx](mdc:src/app/(home)/page.tsx) shows categories in a grid layout.

- **Category Pages**: Located in [src/app/(home)/[category]/page.tsx](mdc:src/app/(home)/[category]/page.tsx).

## Styling

The app uses Tailwind CSS with custom colors defined in [tailwind.config.ts](mdc:tailwind.config.ts). The color scheme includes:

- Primary: Teal/blue-green (#11999E)
- Secondary: Teal/green (#119E7F)
- Accent: Dark teal (#092A2C)

The layout is responsive with mobile-first design principles.
